title: 40 for 40: The 2016 Hawaii Bowl Preview
description:
Number 13 of 40 bowl previews, in which we may not discuss the Hawaii Bowl or the teams playing in it whatsoever! Did you know the cost of living in Honolulu is lower than that in New York City! You won't learn that in the podcast, but you learned about it here, which is almost as good!
